column2: SELECT #  p.objid, s.bestobjid, g.specobjid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g,  p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g,   petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z, s.class, s.z as redshift,   g.oii_#_eqw, g.oii_#_eqw_err, g.h_delta_eqw, g.h_delta_eqw_err,   g.h_alpha_eqw, g.h_alpha_eqw_err, g.nii_#_eqw, g.nii_#_eqw_err,   g.nii_#_eqw, g.nii_#_eqw_err, g.oiii_#_eqw, g.oiii_#_eqw_err,  g.oiii_#_eqw, g.oiii_#_eqw_err, g.oiii_#_eqw, g.oiii_#_eqw FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specObjID = s.specobjid  WHERE   s.class=&&&
